                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-137-off718 t18280110-137-crimeloc721"></join>. On the 5th of January a watchman came in, and I missed a piece of bacon from the top of some cheeses at the door.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-137-person897">
                  RICHARD 
                  ROBERTS
               <interp inst="t18280110-137-person897" type="surname" value="ROBERTS"></interp>
